#### **4. Generic Push-Relabel Algorithm**

Initialize-Preflow(G, s):
  for each vertex v in V:
    h[v] = 0
    e[v] = 0
  for each edge (u, v) in E:
    f(u, v) = 0
  h[s] = |V|
  for each neighbor v of s:
    f(s, v) = c(s, v)
    e[v] = c(s, v)
    e[s] = e[s] - c(s, v)

Push-Relabel(G, s, t):
  Initialize-Preflow(G, s)
  while there exists an active node u:
    if Push is applicable to some edge (u, v):
      Push(u, v)
    else:
      Relabel(u)
  return f  (now a maximum flow)

